title: Tim O'Riordan: The Langer (+Extended) FLAC
description:
"The Langer" was a regional skit-hit several years ago in Ireland, particularly in Cork County, being played on the radio, distributed on CD and played live in celebration of a local slang/curse/insult; "Langer".

This is a FLAC-rip of the "The Langer" single, and includes the Extended version with several more politically-charged verses.
